stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> LocalLookup
    LocalLookup --> AlreadyHeld: 本 Backend 已持有兼容/更强模式
    LocalLookup --> FastPath: 弱 relation lock 且满足条件
    LocalLookup --> MainTable: 需主锁表
    FastPath --> Granted
    MainTable --> Granted: 与 granted 集合及队列兼容
    MainTable --> Waiting: 存在硬/软冲突
    Waiting --> Granted: blocker 释放且轮到本请求
    Waiting --> Aborted: deadlock victim
    Waiting --> Cancelled: lock/statement timeout 或客户端取消
    Granted --> Released: 事务/会话/ResourceOwner 结束
    AlreadyHeld --> Released
    Aborted --> [*]
    Cancelled --> [*]
    Released --> [*]
